%% 5. BACKEND JWT VERIFICATION
flowchart TD
    Req([HTTP Request]) --> Header{Authorization Bearer token?}
    Header -->|No| E401A[401 Missing token]
    Header -->|Yes| Extract[Extract JWT]

    Extract --> Alg{JWT algorithm?}
    Alg -->|HS256| LocalDecode[Decode with SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET audience authenticated]
    Alg -->|RS256 or other| SupaLookup[supabase_admin auth get_user token]

    LocalDecode --> Payload{sub user_id present?}
    SupaLookup --> Payload
    Payload -->|No| E401B[401 Invalid token payload]
    Payload -->|Yes| Verified{require_verified and email not confirmed?}

    Verified -->|Yes| E403[403 EMAIL_NOT_VERIFIED]
    Verified -->|No| OK[Return user_id to router]

    subgraph AuthTiers["Auth Tiers by Endpoint"]
        T1[Public movies chat GET root]
        T2[Token only api users me require_verified false]
        T3[Token plus verified email api recommendations]
    end

