%% 8. WATCHLIST Save Remove Logic Supabase Direct
flowchart TD
    Action([User clicks Watchlist or Save]) --> AuthCheck{Supabase session?}
    AuthCheck -->|No| Modal[Show login modal]
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| AlreadySaved{Already in savedIds?}

    AlreadySaved -->|"Yes remove"| Delete[saved_movies delete by tmdb_id and user_id]
    Delete --> UI1[Update button toast Removed]
    AlreadySaved -->|"No add"| TryRPC

    TryRPC[rpc save_movie_to_wishlist with movie metadata]
    TryRPC -->|success| UI2[Add to savedIds toast Saved]
    TryRPC -->|RPC not found| Fallback

    Fallback[movies upsert then saved_movies insert]
    Fallback -->|RLS error| SQLFix[Run supabase_fix_wishlist.sql]
    Fallback -->|success| UI2

    subgraph DataModel["Supabase Tables"]
        MoviesTable[movies table tmdb_id title poster rating year]
        SavedTable[saved_movies user_id tmdb_id saved_at RLS]
        MoviesTable --> SavedTable
    end

