%% 10. AI RECOMMENDATIONS Frontend Wizard 5 Steps
flowchart TD
    Enter([recommendations.html]) --> AuthGuard{Auth getSession at submit?}
    AuthGuard -->|No| SavePending[Save answers sessionStorage show login modal]
    AuthGuard -->|Yes| Step1

    Step1[Step 1 Genre Action Drama Comedy Horror Sci-fi Romance Thriller Animation]
    Step1 --> Step2[Step 2 Mood Unsettled Inspired Entertained Emotional Thrilled]
    Step2 --> Step3[Step 3 Era Classic 80s-90s 2000s 2010s Recent Any]
    Step3 --> Step4[Step 4 Language English Korean Spanish French Japanese Any]
    Step4 --> Step5[Step 5 Audience Solo Partner Friends Family]

    Step5 --> Submit[Click Get Recommendations]
    Submit --> ReCheck{Session still valid?}
    ReCheck -->|No| Redirect
    ReCheck -->|Yes| API[POST api recommendations generate with JWT and answers]

    API --> Resp{Response}
    Resp -->|200| Results[Render up to 10 movie cards]
    Resp -->|403 EMAIL_NOT_VERIFIED| VerifyMsg[Toast verify email first show banner]
    Resp -->|429| LimitMsg[Toast daily limit 10 per day]
    Resp -->|422 or 502| ErrMsg[Toast validation or AI error]

    Results --> CardClick[Click card to detail.html]
    Results --> StartOver[Start Over reset wizard step 1]

