%% 11. AI RECOMMENDATIONS Backend Pipeline
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Auth as auth.py
    participant Rate as RateLimiter
    participant Rec as recommendation_service
    participant AI as ai_service
    participant TMDB as tmdb_service
    participant DB as SupabaseLogs

    User->>FE: Complete 5-step wizard
    FE->>API: POST recommendations generate with preferences
    API->>Auth: get_user_id_from_request verified email
    Auth-->>API: user_id
    API->>Rate: check rate limit 10 per 24h
    Rate-->>API: OK or 429

    API->>Rec: generate preferences
    Rec->>AI: get_recommendations preferences
    Note over AI: Validate fields call DeepSeek parse JSON up to 15 candidates
    AI-->>Rec: ai_results

    Rec->>TMDB: fetch_all tmdb_ids concurrent
    Note over TMDB: Cache semaphore filter adult normalize fields
    TMDB-->>Rec: enriched movies

    Note over Rec: Verify year tolerance preserve ranking cap at 10 movies
    Rec-->>API: verified movie list

    API->>DB: insert recommendation_logs row
    API-->>FE: movies array
    FE-->>User: Display result grid

